<h2>Plaintext-Only Mode</h2>
<p>The <code>plaintext-only</code> value is ideal when you want editable text without formatting. Pasted content is stripped of all HTML, and keyboard shortcuts like <kbd>Ctrl+B</kbd> have no effect.</p>

