</div>

<h2>Rich Text Editing</h2>
<p>With <code>contenteditable="true"</code>, the browser provides built-in formatting:</p>
<ul>
  <li><kbd>Ctrl+B</kbd> / <kbd>Cmd+B</kbd> for bold</li>
  <li><kbd>Ctrl+I</kbd> / <kbd>Cmd+I</kbd> for italic</li>
  <li><kbd>Ctrl+U</kbd> / <kbd>Cmd+U</kbd> for underline</li>
</ul>

